### Base URL Variable
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### 1. Root Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### 2. Generate Hash (SHA256)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hashing/hash
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Hello CryptoLab!",
  "algorithm": "SHA256"
}

### 3. Calculate Avalanche Effect
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hashing/avalanche
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text1": "CryptoLab",
  "text2": "CryptoLab!",
  "algorithm": "SHA256"
}

### 4. Password Strength & Entropy
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/passwords/strength
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "P@ssw0rd2026!$"
}

### 5. Generate Salt
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/passwords/generate-salt
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Hash Password (Argon2id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/passwords/hash
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "MySuperSecurePass123!",
  "algorithm": "argon2id"
}

### 7. Generate Symmetric Key (AES-256)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/symmetric/generate-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "algorithm": "AES",
  "key_size": 256
}

### 8. Encrypt Message (AES-GCM)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/symmetric/encrypt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plaintext": "Confidential Payload Data",
  "key": "63617473617265636f6f6c313233343536373839303132333435363738393031",
  "algorithm": "AES",
  "mode": "GCM"
}

### 9. Generate RSA Keypair
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/asymmetric/generate-rsa
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key_size": 2048
}

### 10. Analyze SSL Certificate
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/certificate/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "google.com"
}

### 11. Explorer Supported Algorithms
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/explorer/algorithms
Accept: application/json

### 12. List Challenges
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/challenges/list
Accept: application/json

### 13. Get User Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/challenges/status/testuser
Accept: application/json

### 14. Submit Challenge Answer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/challenges/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "challenge_id": 1,
  "answer_index": 1
}
